<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 16:07:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“我确信我再也不会走路了。现在我正在为欧洲锦标赛进行训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-sure-id-never-walk-again-now-im-practicing-for-the-european-championships/0000018e-edcf-dd51-a79e-ffdf3b6e0000</link><description>自 2019 年成立以来，以色列截肢足球队为失去一条腿的年轻人提供了再次踢球的机会。现在，那些在 10 月 7 日受伤和在战斗中受伤的人已经加入了他们的行列。 “没有什么比能够和他们一起打球更能让我康复了，”新队员 Shaked Biton 说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 06:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-sure-id-never-walk-again-now-im-practicing-for-the-european-championships/0000018e-edcf-dd51-a79e-ffdf3b6e0000</guid></item><item><title>正统派对本格维尔的战争是关于权力、金钱和嫉妒的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-war-on-ben-gvir-is-about-power-money-and-jealousy/0000018e-f131-dfe0-a1af-f1fdda740000</link><description>由于对极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本格维尔的政治好战行为越来越不满，内塔尼亚胡联盟内部的冲突加剧</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 06:15:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-war-on-ben-gvir-is-about-power-money-and-jealousy/0000018e-f131-dfe0-a1af-f1fdda740000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦环卫工人因敢于爬上自家屋顶而被以色列狙击手射杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-palestinian-is-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper-for-daring-to-go-up-on-his-roof/0000018e-f9a5-d6a0-a9ef-f9bd171b0000</link><description>一名居住在约旦河西岸难民营的贫困工人被以色列士兵枪杀三天后，他的儿子出生并以他的名字命名</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 04:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-palestinian-is-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper-for-daring-to-go-up-on-his-roof/0000018e-f9a5-d6a0-a9ef-f9bd171b0000</guid></item><item><title>这个审查机构禁止阿拉伯和反占领电影，几十年来塑造了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/banning-arab-and-anti-occupation-films-this-censorship-agency-shaped-israel-for-decades/0000018e-f970-db42-a99f-fdffd2a90000</link><description>回顾以色列电影和戏剧审查委员会的历史，就会发现它在塑造这个年轻国家的文化形象以及我们的世界观方面发挥着重要作用</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:53:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/banning-arab-and-anti-occupation-films-this-censorship-agency-shaped-israel-for-decades/0000018e-f970-db42-a99f-fdffd2a90000</guid></item><item><title>报告：三名真主党特工在黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生；六枚火箭弹射入以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article-live/iran-says-it-will-respond-at-maximum-level-if-israel-acts-against-its-interests/0000018e-f93c-d6a0-a9ef-f9bc73da0000</link><description>在巴格达附近亲伊朗民兵基地的一次空袭中，造成 1 人死亡、6 人受伤 ■ 加沙哈马斯扣押的人质的家人抗议要求释放；封锁主要高速公路 ■ 以色列官员向《华盛顿邮报》证实对伊朗进行空袭 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，三名伊朗官员表示，以色列的空袭袭击了伊朗西部伊斯法罕附近的军事基地</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:30:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article-live/iran-says-it-will-respond-at-maximum-level-if-israel-acts-against-its-interests/0000018e-f93c-d6a0-a9ef-f9bc73da0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人想知道为什么袭击他们的定居者费力遮住自己的脸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-wonder-why-settlers-who-attack-them-bother-concealing-their-faces/0000018e-ec89-dd51-a79e-fe99e35c0000</link><description>本雅明·阿希梅尔在约旦河西岸被谋杀，引发了军队保护下的定居者暴力浪潮。但这只是定居者在小范围内不断做的事情的借口：散布恐惧、暴力攻击村民和破坏财产</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-wonder-why-settlers-who-attack-them-bother-concealing-their-faces/0000018e-ec89-dd51-a79e-fe99e35c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院下令释放涉嫌煽动恐怖的巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-release-of-palestinian-academic-suspected-of-incitement-to-terror/0000018e-f760-d79f-a98e-f7e471360000</link><description>法官批评警方，称没有理由因 Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授关于 10 月 7 日的言论而逮捕她。警方辩称，她“利用阴谋来推进针对以色列的措施”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 21:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-release-of-palestinian-academic-suspected-of-incitement-to-terror/0000018e-f760-d79f-a98e-f7e471360000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列将注意力集中在伊朗，与哈马斯的人质协议变得不那么重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-focus-on-iran-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas-becomes-a-low-priority/0000018e-f701-d79f-a98e-f785c5fe0000</link><description>随着约旦河西岸的暴力升级失控，与哈马斯的谈判中一张又一张的牌都丢失了。 加沙战争结束后，以色列军队将不得不解决弹药短缺问题，并像真主党那样加强预备役部队。尝试哈马斯式的入侵</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-israels-focus-on-iran-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas-becomes-a-low-priority/0000018e-f701-d79f-a98e-f785c5fe0000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列对伊朗的袭击保持距离，专注于缓和局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-distances-itself-from-israels-strike-in-iran-focusing-on-deescalation-efforts/0000018e-f6d3-d87e-a58e-f7f3f7ab0000</link><description>据报道，以色列周五早上袭击了伊朗境内的目标后，美国很快否认参与了这些事件。意大利七国集团峰会期间，布林肯强调美国对以色列国防的承诺，并宣布七国集团联合制裁伊朗武器工业</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:03:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-distances-itself-from-israels-strike-in-iran-focusing-on-deescalation-efforts/0000018e-f6d3-d87e-a58e-f7f3f7ab0000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官认为以色列对伊朗的反应是相称的，不会导致局势升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-believe-israeli-response-to-iran-is-proportionate-wont-escalate-region/0000018e-f6aa-d87e-a58e-f7aaf1060000</link><description>几位外交官表示，他们的国家最近几天与以色列就打击伊朗问题举行了会谈，试图防止冲突升级。一位外交官表示，危险尚未过去，“但仍有谨慎乐观的空间”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-believe-israeli-response-to-iran-is-proportionate-wont-escalate-region/0000018e-f6aa-d87e-a58e-f7aaf1060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 196 天：世界敦促以色列和伊朗在伊斯法罕袭击后缓和紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-196-world-urges-israel-iran-to-de-escalate-after-isfahan-strike/0000018e-f730-df38-abbf-ffb82d050000</link><description>国际媒体报道，以色列袭击了伊朗城市伊斯法罕附近的空军基地 ■ 官方媒体报道，伊朗高级官员称袭击没有造成任何损害，没有计划立即进行报复 ■ 美国、欧盟制裁以色列极右活动人士和非政府组织 ■ 评级机构标准普尔全球评级下调以色列的长期评级 ■ 美国否决了联合国安理会给予巴勒斯坦权力机构正式成员地位的提议 ■ 战争结束 196 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 16:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-196-world-urges-israel-iran-to-de-escalate-after-isfahan-strike/0000018e-f730-df38-abbf-ffb82d050000</guid></item><item><title>美国和欧盟制裁以色列著名极右活动人士和为先前受制裁的西岸定居者筹款的非政府组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-eu-sanction-settler-leaders-ngos-that-fundraised-for-sanctioned-settlers/0000018e-f6a2-d79f-a98e-f7a6408f0000</link><description>在约旦河西岸暴力升级的背景下，美国宣布对以色列极右翼人士和团体实施新的制裁，特别是两个极右翼非政府组织，因为它们为此前受到美国制裁的定居者筹款。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-eu-sanction-settler-leaders-ngos-that-fundraised-for-sanctioned-settlers/0000018e-f6a2-d79f-a98e-f7a6408f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争看不到结束的迹象，以色列的评级下调可能只是一个开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-no-end-to-the-war-in-sight-israels-rating-downgrade-could-just-be-the-beginning/0000018e-f62e-df38-abbf-feae8dea0000</link><description>标准普尔的决定暴露了人们真正的担忧，即降级将改变投资者对以色列经济的情绪。如果以色列有一位能够在战时内阁内部做出经济决策的专业财政部长，这将会有所帮助</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-no-end-to-the-war-in-sight-israels-rating-downgrade-could-just-be-the-beginning/0000018e-f62e-df38-abbf-feae8dea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对伊斯法罕的无声打击表明内塔尼亚胡对伊朗和加沙没有战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-muted-strike-on-isfahan-shows-netanyahu-has-no-strategy-on-iran-as-well-as-gaza/0000018e-f623-df38-abbf-feab83690000</link><description>以色列对伊斯法罕的平淡打击至多只是一种临时措施，一种占位性措施。这是内塔尼亚胡下令的，他以谈论伊朗威胁为职业，但当关键时刻到来时，他无话可说或提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:54:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-muted-strike-on-isfahan-shows-netanyahu-has-no-strategy-on-iran-as-well-as-gaza/0000018e-f623-df38-abbf-feab83690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对伊朗袭击的反应影响拉法行动的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-response-to-iranian-attack-impacts-legitimacy-of-an-operation-in-rafah/0000018e-f5c4-d87e-a58e-f5e6cf2f0000</link><description>据报道，埃及和巴勒斯坦权力机构已经接受以色列将进入拉法的事实，并开始准备吸纳流离失所者和管理民政。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 11:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-response-to-iranian-attack-impacts-legitimacy-of-an-operation-in-rafah/0000018e-f5c4-d87e-a58e-f5e6cf2f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗给了内塔尼亚胡前所未有的机会，但他是错失机会的冠军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/iran-gave-netanyahu-an-unprecedented-opportunity-but-hes-a-pro-at-missing-opportunities/0000018e-f2b0-d240-a19f-f6b31d610000</link><description>伊朗一周前的袭击给了以色列重新获得西方世界青睐的机会。以色列的克制会被证明是审慎的吗？ ■ 事情变得越来越清楚：战争结束前人质不会返回 ■ 甘茨继续与内塔尼亚胡合作 ■ 极右翼分子斯莫特里奇遭遇不那么即时的因果报应</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 10:24:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/iran-gave-netanyahu-an-unprecedented-opportunity-but-hes-a-pro-at-missing-opportunities/0000018e-f2b0-d240-a19f-f6b31d610000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗表示，如果以色列采取违背其利益的行动，伊朗将做出“最大程度”的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</link><description>巴格达附近亲伊朗民兵基地遭空袭，造成 1 人死亡、6 人受伤 ■ 伊朗外长表示，如果以色列采取违背其利益的行动，伊朗将做出“最大程度”的回应 ■ 人质家属抗议要求释放人质；封锁主要高速公路 ■ 以色列官员向《华盛顿邮报》证实对伊朗进行空袭 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，三名伊朗官员称袭击袭击了伊朗西部伊斯法罕附近的军事基地 ■ 美国对伊朗无人机计划、钢铁、汽车工业实施新制裁 ■ 欧盟和美国对定居者领导人、非政府组织实施制裁</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道伊朗空军基地在以色列袭击中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</link><description>伊朗电视台称，在宣布防空系统已启动后，核设施在报道中的袭击中未受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在威尼斯双年展以色列馆外抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</link><description>在这场著名的艺术活动中，亲巴勒斯坦抗议者指责以色列实施种族灭绝，而活动人士则在城市各处悬挂了 40 件巴勒斯坦艺术家的作品</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 00:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔下调以色列信用评级，理由是与伊朗的军事升级风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</link><description>负面前景反映了以色列与哈马斯战争以及与真主党或伊朗的对抗可能对以色列经济的影响超过该机构目前预期的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>